Kipi-plugins 0.3.0 - Release date: 11/05/2009
------------------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES:

General         : Fix compilation under MSVC 9.
PicasaWebExport : Support protected albums (sign-in required to view).
PrintImages     : Added per photo print management.
PrintImages     : Added Atkins page layout printing.

BUGFIXES FROM KDE BUGZILLA (alias B.K.O | http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 186981 : FlickrExport       : Flickr on plasma crashes on "next photo".
